      "split": "tune",
      "kind": "audit-output",
      "prompt": "Security audit this endpoint summary: `/search` builds SQL with an f-string using user-controlled `q` in a LIKE query; a nearby `/admin/stats` query already uses bind parameters. Report only evidence-backed findings.",
      "expected_behavior": [
